; CHECKTUPLE arm pruning: top-down checker procedures populate the present /
; absent / unknown arms; @differential recursion (transitive closure) makes
; the unknown state reachable, and the absent arm typically collapses to a
; no-op and is pruned while present/unknown survive.

#message add_edge(u32 From, u32 To) @differential.
#local edge(u32 From, u32 To).
#local path(u32 From, u32 To).
#query reachable(bound u32 From, bound u32 To).

edge(F, T) : add_edge(F, T).
path(F, T) : edge(F, T).
path(F, T) : edge(F, X), path(X, T).
reachable(F, T) : path(F, T).
